# game/Scenes/Izzy/IzzyDates/izzyarcadedate.rpy:30
translate portuguese izzyarcadedatestart_515d2991:

    # gl "What's up, Twig. Let's go play some games."
    gl "E aí, Twig. Vamos jogar uns jogos."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/IzzyDates/izzyarcadedate.rpy:36
translate portuguese izzyarcadedatestart_605a4d9f:

    # gl "Hey, this place is pretty cool. I bet Stanley and Paul would love it."
    gl "Ei, este sítio é muito fixe. Aposto que o Stanley e o Paul iam adorar."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/IzzyDates/izzyarcadedate.rpy:37
translate portuguese izzyarcadedatestart_b1581a15:

    # gl "Maybe we could bring them sometime, when I'm able to."
    gl "Talvez possamos trazê-los um dia destes, quando eu puder."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/IzzyDates/izzyarcadedate.rpy:38
translate portuguese izzyarcadedatestart_8de112f2:

    # pc "Yeah for sure, that sounds fun."
    pc "Sim, com certeza, parece divertido."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/IzzyDates/izzyarcadedate.rpy:45
translate portuguese izzyarcadedatestart_f9357be7:

    # "We play games and chat for a while."
    "Jogamos e conversamos um bocado."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/IzzyDates/izzyarcadedate.rpy:49
translate portuguese izzyarcadedatestart_66506ca5:

    # "We try out a few different games."
    "Experimentamos alguns jogos diferentes."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/IzzyDates/izzyarcadedate.rpy:57
translate portuguese izzyarcadedatestart_726fbd6c:

    # "It's all fun and she seems to have a good time."
    "É tudo divertido e ela parece estar a divertir-se."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/IzzyDates/izzyarcadedate.rpy:59
translate portuguese izzyarcadedatestart_84d584ed:

    # "When we're done playing, I drive Izzy back to her house."
    "Quando acabamos de jogar, levo a Izzy de volta a casa dela."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/IzzyDates/izzyarcadedate.rpy:60
translate portuguese izzyarcadedatestart_2a5b6b89:

    # "I pull into her driveway and she turns to look at me."
    "Encosto na entrada da garagem e ela vira-se para olhar para mim."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/IzzyDates/izzyarcadedate.rpy:62
translate portuguese izzyarcadedatestart_6dd86d8c:

    # gl "So, do you want to come inside and fuck a little?"
    gl "Então, queres entrar e foder um pouco?"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/IzzyDates/izzyarcadedate.rpy:69
translate portuguese izzyarcadedatestart_dcbc938c:

    # gl "Cool, let's go."
    gl "Fixe, vamos lá."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/IzzyDates/izzyarcadedate.rpy:72
translate portuguese izzyarcadedatestart_dcbc938c_1:

    # gl "Cool, let's go."
    gl "Fixe, vamos lá."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/IzzyDates/izzyarcadedate.rpy:75
translate portuguese izzyarcadedatestart_7c186cf5:

    # gl "Damn. Well thanks for hanging out anyway. It was fun."
    gl "Raios. Bem, obrigado por teres saído comigo na mesma. Foi divertido."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/IzzyDates/izzyarcadedate.rpy:76
translate portuguese izzyarcadedatestart_63fc4244:

    # pc "Bye, Izzy."
    pc "Adeus, Izzy."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/IzzyDates/izzyarcadedate.rpy:79
translate portuguese izzyarcadedatestart_8b93ebfd:

    # "I wait until she gets out and walks into her house before I drive away."
    "Espero até ela sair e entrar em casa antes de me ir embora."

